title: 136. Execute Execute Execute Ft. Chadd Wright
itunes:title: 136. Execute Execute Execute Ft. Chadd Wright
description: All of us are here on Earth for a reason. On today's episode, Andy and the guys are joined by former Navy SEAL turned entrepreneur and ultra-runner, Chadd Wright as they discuss the mindset of someone who never quits working towards their goals, the situation brewing in Afghanistan and how you can learn to detach yourself from an identity to help you see the truth.
